data.description: Contemporary ranch on nearly half an acre in Navarre! This property is like 2 lots in 1 with 0.46 acres allowing for a spacious home plus a large and private backyard. Just up the street from the Publix shopping plaza and minutes to Hwy 98, this home is conveniently located to all Navarre has to offer including Hurlburt Field and of course gorgeous Navarre Beach! Inside offers about 1,350 square feet including three bedrooms, two bathrooms, and an floorplan living room, dining area, and kitchen. Flowing tile floors and soaring ceilings connect the living areas and create a big, open layout. The living area features cathedral ceilings, a stone fireplace for the upcoming cool evenings, and french doors to the back porch. Overlooking the living room is the kitchen which offers stainless steel appliances, a contemporary color palette, and a long breakfast bar for casual dining. Split from the guest bedrooms and bathroom is the private primary suite. It has a walk-in closet and a separate entrance to the backyard, plus an ensuite bathroom with an L shaped vanity and beautiful glass door shower. Out back is the expansive yard which is surrounded by mature shade trees and a privacy fence for the kids and pets to safely play. With a 2 year old roof, this house is move-in ready!
